26:45.647 --> 26:47.475
What do they say?

26:47.649 --> 26:49.869
Big fish, small pond.

26:51.522 --> 26:54.395
But we are the sea.

26:56.484 --> 26:57.485
Mm.

26:57.659 --> 26:59.966
I can tell you are thinking,

27:00.140 --> 27:03.491
you can just kill me
the way you kill the men before.

27:03.665 --> 27:05.667
But this is a mistake.

27:05.841 --> 27:07.843
Because when you look at me,

27:08.017 --> 27:10.498
you don't see the man behind me.

27:10.672 --> 27:13.283
And the man behind him.

27:13.457 --> 27:15.895
And all the men that follow.

27:18.332 --> 27:20.160
Forever.

27:28.516 --> 27:30.518
Mm-hmm?

27:30.692 --> 27:32.520
You see them now.

27:32.694 --> 27:34.653
The wave that never ends.

27:36.698 --> 27:38.439
We understand each other.

27:38.613 --> 27:40.571
Cheer up.

27:40.746 --> 27:42.965
Look at it this way:
we are not taking half,

27:43.139 --> 27:45.098
we are leaving half.

27:47.230 --> 27:49.406
You work for us now.

27:49.580 --> 27:52.279
You do what we say
or we kill you

27:52.453 --> 27:54.847
and find someone who will.

