33:15.602 --> 33:18.953
ETHELRIDA:
History is a form of memory.

33:19.127 --> 33:22.261
But what does it mean
to remember?

33:23.653 --> 33:26.221
We think, naturally,
of our own past,

33:26.395 --> 33:28.093
our lives day by day,

33:28.267 --> 33:31.922
and through them we see
the events of our times.

33:32.097 --> 33:33.881
