33:34.055 --> 33:36.579
We are Black and white,

33:36.753 --> 33:39.669
rich and poor,

33:39.843 --> 33:43.021
foreign-born and domestic.

33:44.544 --> 33:48.156
And yet,
if our pasts are separate,

33:48.330 --> 33:51.246
then aren't our histories
separate, too?

33:51.420 --> 33:53.379
Segregated?

33:55.468 --> 33:56.904
Ask yourself:

33:57.078 --> 33:59.559
who writes the books?

33:59.733 --> 34:03.302
Who chooses what we remember
and what gets forgotten?

34:05.869 --> 34:08.350
My name
is Ethelrida Pearl Smutny.

34:08.524 --> 34:11.484
